","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/txUBJZ9Jk9C1ynnia4nSyHEMive.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/oC2CXLsk14d6TwcA5KDRgooTbNA.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/jauPPS1owYApArdEQOVhITq1LbO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/hYvY2q1CHPN9qah1g5af6HaCZhc.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/eJMZTw3Bu9IzTcPb3qYyZuggpxX.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/r2LToVWpuK3T5XrUGFwlTJVdKXi.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/2YJRoNlhY7NynvJfAn0jxMb9Aik.jpg","iso_639_1":"ko","vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/gqCFtXhmHtRS84d54Sfhy5oiksq.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:57:57.528+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"제발 조용히 좀 해주세요, 그 입을 찢어버리기 전에","homepage":"","overview":"내 집 마련에 성공한 주영과 주희 자매. 어느 날부터 아파트 어딘가에서 들려오는 정체불명의 층간소음에 시달린다. 그러던 중 동생 주희와 연락이 끊기자 불안에 휩싸인 주영은 급히 지방 공장에서 집으로 돌아오고, 주희의 남자친구 기훈과 함께 실종된 동생을 추적하기 시작한다. 한편, 자매와 마찬가지로 층간소음에 시달리던 아랫집 남자는 그 소음의 근원이 윗집 자매에게 있다고 생각해 살인 협박을 하게 되는데…."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Noise","runtime":95,"tagline":"Could you be quiet before I rip your mouth out.","homepage":"","overview":"Ju-young is a young woman with a hearing impediment who decides to investigate her sister's inexplicable disappearance, last seen in her apartment. Feeling more and more cornered, Ju-young begins to hear strange sounds and sense an evil presence in the apartment."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"噪音杀机","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"讲述了两姐妹艰难入住的公寓后，妹妹消失得无影无踪后的事件。姐姐“珠英”（李先彬饰演）和妹妹的男朋友“奇勋”（金玟锡饰演）一起，为了寻找噪音的真实身份和妹妹，在公寓里寻找过程中发生难以置信恐怖的故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Паранормальное явление. Шум","runtime":104,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Две сестры недавно переехали. Когда одна из них бесследно исчезает прямо из квартиры, вторая начинает поиски. Кажется, с этим связан загадочный шум."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"家嘈屋斃","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"患聽力障礙的姊姊某日接獲來電，得知妹妹竟離奇失蹤。她重返兩人曾同住的公寓尋找線索，卻漸漸被捲進恐懼的漩渦中。妹妹曾抱怨樓上傳來怪異噪音，如今自己也開始聽見詭異聲響，甚至收到鄰居恐嚇，指控她才是噪音的源頭。公寓流竄的怪聲似乎與妹妹失蹤有著密不可分的關聯……取材自韓國社會常見的「層間噪音」問題，由《酒鬼都市女人們》李先彬獨挑大樑，夥拍《太陽的後裔》金珉錫，以精湛演技詮釋都市人的共同惡夢，成就南韓年度最賣座驚栗片。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Шум","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Жінка з вадами слуху переслідується загадковими звуками, пов’язаними зі зникненням її сестри та появою зловісного духа. Це приводить до моторошної таємниці й веде до розкриття загадкової сутності."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"เสียงซ่อนผี","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หญิงสาวหนูหนวกคนหนึ่งถูกตามหลอกหลอนโดยเสียงที่เชื่อมโยงกับการหายตัวไปของพี่สาวของเธอ และการมีตัวตนอยู่ของวิญญานที่ชั่วร้าย นำไปสู่การค้นพบความลับดำมืดและการเปิดเผยซึ่งตัวตนอันลึกลับ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Tiếng Ồn Quỷ Dị","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"TIẾNG ỒN QUỶ DỊ là câu chuyện về hai chị em Joo Young và Joo Hee. Sau khi dọn vào căn hộ mới, cả hai liên tục bị quấy nhiễu bởi những tiếng động kỳ quái phát ra từ giữa các tầng – thứ âm thanh âm ỉ, vặn vẹo như thể có ai đó… hoặc thứ gì đó đang sống giữa các bức tường. Rồi một ngày, Joo Hee biến mất không dấu vết. Joo Young cùng bạn trai của em gái lao vào cuộc truy tìm trong vô vọng – khi càng đào sâu, họ càng tiến gần đến một bí mật đen tối bị chôn vùi sau những bức tường cách âm. Cùng lúc đó, người đàn ông sống tầng dưới cũng bị tra tấn bởi chính thứ âm thanh đó và tin rằng, con quái vật nằm ngay trong căn hộ của hai chị em."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"噪音殺機","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"有聽力障礙的姊姊珠英，與妹妹珠憘終於買下夢寐以求的新房，沒想到噩夢才正要降臨。珠憘開始被來自公寓某處的神秘噪音折磨得身心俱疲。那讓人不耐的樓層噪音，不僅讓她無法安睡，更像是潛藏某種秘密的警告。正當珠英離家工作時，妹妹突然失蹤，讓驚慌失措的珠英立刻趕回家，並與珠憘的男友基勳聯手追查真相…。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Noise","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dwie siostry wprowadzają się do nowego mieszkania, ale radość z przeprowadzki szybko psują męczące i tajemnicze dźwięki. Wkrótce jedna z kobiet znika bez śladu, a szukająca jej zrozpaczona siostra zaczyna otrzymywać śmiertelne groźby."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Ruídos","runtime":95,"tagline":"Mesmo que você não os veja... Você vai ouvi-los.","homepage":"https://a2filmes.com.br/details/2994","overview":"Decidida a desvendar o mistério do desaparecimento de sua irmã, uma jovem com deficiência auditiva inicia uma investigação própria. O que começa como uma busca por respostas rapidamente se transforma em um pesadelo: ela passa a perceber sons estranhos e a notar uma presença maligna que a cerca, revelando uma nova e aterrorizante dimensão de sua deficiência."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"ضجيج","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"جو-يونغ شابة تعاني من إعاقة سمعية، تقرر التحقيق في الاختفاء الغامض لشقيقتها، التي شوهدت آخر مرة في شقتها. ومع ازدياد شعورها بالحصار، تبدأ جو-يونغ بسماع أصوات غريبة واستشعار وجود شرير داخل الشقة."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Noise: Sonidos del más allá","runtime":93,"tagline":"¿Podrías estar tranquilo antes de que te arranque la boca?","homepage":"","overview":"Joo‑young, quien padece pérdida auditiva, vive con su hermana Joo‑hee en un edificio nuevo. De pronto, Joo‑hee desaparece y Joo‑young, alarmada, regresa desde el campo para buscarla. Pronto descubre que ruidos inexplicables emanan de las paredes, sumiéndola en una pesadilla sensorial que revela verdades horribles escondidas entre los muros."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Noise","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Une femme malentendante est hantée par des sons liés à la disparition de sa sœur et à la présence d'un esprit malveillant."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Noise: Lanetin Sesi","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Noise - Hörst du es auch?","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ju-young ist eine junge Frau mit einer Hörbehinderung, die beschließt, das unerklärliche Verschwinden ihrer Schwester zu untersuchen, die zuletzt in ihrer Wohnung gesehen wurde. Immer mehr in die Enge getrieben, beginnt Ju-young, seltsame Geräusche zu hören und eine unheimliche Präsenz in der Wohnung zu spüren."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"68917191b5d398a3f57cff5b","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68917191b5d398a3f57cff5b","author":"Chris Sawin","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-08-05T02:50:57.630Z","updated_at":"2025-08-05T02:50:57.699Z","author_details":{"name":"Chris Sawin","rating":6,"username":"ChrisSawin","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1145221,"adult":false,"title":"It Feeds","video":false,"overview":"A clairvoyant therapist confronts her own personal demons while trying to save a young girl who believes a malevolent entity is feeding on her.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.0031,"vote_count":195,"poster_path":"/uC3lzzgOUgkubje7HR20qznAAGj.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-17","vote_average":6.715,"backdrop_path":"/vyJxZSLdgCmUEZlc6OhyJUDqTjA.jpg","original_title":"It Feeds","original_language":"en"},{"id":624779,"adult":false,"title":"VFW","video":false,"overview":"A typical night for veterans at a VFW turns into an all-out battle for survival when a desperate teen runs into the bar with a bag of stolen drugs. When a gang of violent punks come looking for her, the vets use every weapon at their disposal to protect the girl and themselves from an unrelenting attack.","genre_ids":[28,80,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0407,"vote_count":259,"poster_path":"/AnVD7Gn14uOTQhcc5xYZGQ9DRvS.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-21","vote_average":5.871,"backdrop_path":"/qhGHcg1RxrAObpabDu03MkxCI1G.jpg","original_title":"VFW","original_language":"en"},{"id":1355666,"adult":false,"title":"Love Untangled","video":false,"overview":"A lovestruck teen plans to win the school heartthrob by going from curly to straight hair — until a new transfer student changes everything.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3337,"vote_count":164,"poster_path":"/e7jStO2xfBUAUK37LbINHd1qtgy.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-28","vote_average":8.369,"backdrop_path":"/oBcvmHD7lbaX8RZ7NXvO05fIJef.jpg","original_title":"고백의 역사","original_language":"ko"},{"id":939914,"adult":false,"title":"Glorious","video":false,"overview":"After a breakup, Wes ends up at a remote rest stop. He finds himself locked inside the bathroom with a mysterious figure speaking from an adjacent stall. Soon Wes realizes he is involved in a situation more terrible than he could imagine.","genre_ids":[27,14,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.2223,"vote_count":193,"poster_path":"/gttZLC3yhLFx1EnfjEUaDb2YAwl.jpg","release_date":"2022-07-21","vote_average":5.824,"backdrop_path":"/up8mHTvnn92bqcq3paWbFdWWXXz.jpg","original_title":"Glorious","original_language":"en"},{"id":1095805,"adult":false,"title":"Stuntman","video":false,"overview":"A washed-up action choreographer, struggling to find his way in a changing industry, risks everything to stage an epic comeback, and attempts to repair the relationship with his estranged daughter before it's too late.","genre_ids":[18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6875,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/u7gxec9lnbInTgoEG7oWZVgfSOI.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-14","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/DlXdNS5JmM5WPSk5H64ritDy5.jpg","original_title":"武替道","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1159472,"adult":false,"title":"Shame on Dry Land","video":false,"overview":"In the shade of Malta’s scorching sun, around the edges of the Swedish online-gambling community, exiled con man Dimman shows up for a lavish wedding, kicking off a desperate and decadent pursuit of redemption.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2271,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/1jIIN2V5QaCnpsl2LrmIvzSWo8F.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-24","vote_average":5.333,"backdrop_path":"/xWQZ7FTo3s9C9v8E2jkoA7foQ0N.jpg","original_title":"Syndabocken","original_language":"sv"},{"id":1119878,"adult":false,"title":"Ice Road: Vengeance","video":false,"overview":"Big rig ice road driver Mike McCann travels to Nepal to scatter his late brother’s ashes on Mt. Everest. While on a packed tour bus traversing the deadly 12,000 ft. terrain of the infamous Road to the Sky, McCann and his mountain guide encounter a group of mercenaries and must fight to save themselves, the busload of innocent travelers, and the local villagers’ homeland.","genre_ids":[28,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.0592,"vote_count":574,"poster_path":"/cQN9rZj06rXMVkk76UF1DfBAico.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-27","vote_average":6.254,"backdrop_path":"/2nwhxEyefcIFKwOrSigiamoIzu2.jpg","original_title":"Ice Road: Vengeance","original_language":"en"},{"id":324544,"adult":false,"title":"In the Lost Lands","video":false,"overview":"A queen sends the powerful and feared sorceress Gray Alys to the ghostly wilderness of the Lost Lands in search of a magical power, where she and her guide, the drifter Boyce, must outwit and outfight both man and demon.","genre_ids":[28,14,37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.9431,"vote_count":725,"poster_path":"/dDlfjR7gllmr8HTeN6rfrYhTdwX.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-27","vote_average":6.412,"backdrop_path":"/eOKpbUpd178x9Z2grd3vC74kkkU.jpg","original_title":"In the Lost Lands","original_language":"en"},{"id":803796,"adult":false,"title":"KPop Demon Hunters","video":false,"overview":"When K-pop superstars Rumi, Mira and Zoey aren't selling out stadiums, they're using their secret powers to protect their fans from supernatural threats.","genre_ids":[14,10402,35,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":43.7242,"vote_count":2401,"poster_path":"/zT7Lhw3BhJbMkRqm9Zlx2YGMsY0.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-20","vote_average":8.091,"backdrop_path":"/w3Bi0wygeFQctn6AqFTwhGNXRwL.jpg","original_title":"KPop Demon Hunters","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":21.4528,"vote_count":11366,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.036,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":76600,"adult":false,"title":"Avatar: The Way of Water","video":false,"overview":"Set more than a decade after the events of the first film, learn the story of the Sully family (Jake, Neytiri, and their kids), the trouble that follows them, the lengths they go to keep each other safe, the battles they fight to stay alive, and the tragedies they endure.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie",